    LoginQRCode is the QR code that users can use to login to their account on another device

    QRCode
    QRCode is the super class from which GameQRCode and LoginQRCode subclasses extend from This class will take the string contents of a QR code and convert it into a SHA256 hash This hash is stored into the protected variable `hash`
